{
  "If a car's velocity is v(t) = 3t^2 - 12t + 9 m/s, at what times is the car momentarily at rest?": "如果汽车的速度是 v(t) = 3t%2 - 12t + 9 m/s, 什么时候汽车可以暂时休息?",
