  "The rate of oil leaking from a pipeline is R(t) = 1000/(1 + t)^2 barrels per day. How many barrels leak in the first 9 days?": "从输油管漏油的速度是R(t) = 1000/(1+t)2桶/日。前9天有多少桶漏油?",
