  "If f(x) is continuous and integral from 0 to 5 of f(x) dx = 12, and integral from 0 to 3 of f(x) dx = 7, then integral from 3 to 5 of f(x) dx =": "如果 f(x) 是连续的, 从0到5的 f(x) dx = 12, 从0到3的 f(x) dx = 7, 然后从3到5的 f(x) dx =",
