  "$1000": "1 000 000美元",
  "Cost = integral from 50 to 100 of (20 + 0.1x) dx = [20x + 0.05x^2] from 50 to 100 = (2000 + 500) - (1000 + 125) = 2500 - 1125 = $1375.": "成本=50至100(20+0.1xx)dx=[20x+0.05xxx],50至100=(2000+500)-(1 000+125)=2 500-1125=1375)之间50至100(20+0.1x)dx=[20x+0.05xxxxxx2],50至100(2000+500)-(1 000+125)=2 500-1125=1 175。",
  "The rate of temperature change in a room is T'(t) = -2 + 0.5t degrees per hour. If T(0) = 72 degrees F, what is the temperature at t = 4?": "房间温度变化的速率是 T'(t) = -2 + 0.5吨/小时。如果 T(0) = 72 °F,那么t = 4的温度是多少?",
